      <title>南苏丹央行维持基准利率 15%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/south-sudan-s-central-bank-retains-key-interest-rate-at-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南苏丹行长约翰尼·奥希萨·达米安表示，南苏丹货币政策委员会同意将央行基准利率维持在 15%。]]></description>
