      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 01:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国出口势头因中国需求而增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/south-korea-s-export-momentum-grows-on-demand-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国需求增加且半导体销售保持强劲，韩国12月份出口保持增长势头。]]></description>
