    <item>
      <title>在债权人强烈反对后，Big Lots 获准批准救助协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/big-lots-wins-approval-of-rescue-deal-after-creditor-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产零售商 Big Lots Inc. 获得法院批准的救助协议，以挽救其部分门店免于关闭，尽管供应商声称该协议不公平地使他们承受了巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/big-lots-wins-approval-of-rescue-deal-after-creditor-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年 10,000 美元在一系列杰出投资中的表现如何</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/how-10-000-fared-in-2024-across-a-range-of-standout-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲和中东的战争。全球政治动荡。对美国可能陷入经济衰退的担忧。这些和其他陷阱在 2024 年困扰着市场，但最终，敢于冒险的投资者获得了回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/how-10-000-fared-in-2024-across-a-range-of-standout-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 23:39:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>协议到期后俄罗斯天然气通过乌克兰向欧洲输送停止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/russian-gas-flow-to-europe-via-ukraine-set-to-halt-as-time-runs-out-for-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一项重要过境协议到期，俄罗斯经乌克兰向欧洲输送的天然气中断，这加大了欧洲大陆能源安全的风险，因为欧洲大陆严重依赖天然气储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/russian-gas-flow-to-europe-via-ukraine-set-to-halt-as-time-runs-out-for-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 15:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
